scene.message:
Yukino: Somehow this room{nl}
has an unpleasant feel.{nl}
Like we're being watched{waitkey}by malicious eyes...{waitkey}{ret}

???: Ohohohoho!{nl}
Good day to you all.{nl}
How splendid of you to{waitkey}grace this tower.{waitkey}{clearbox}I welcome you from the{nl}
heart. Ohohohohoho!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Who's there!?{nl}
Show yourself! No doubt{nl}
just some keeper of{nl}
this tower!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Put on airs all you like,{nl}
you're nothing but a small{nl}
fry - a "fox borrowing the{waitkey}tiger's might" from{nl}
the Snow Queen!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Who? Show yourself!{nl}
You're likely this tower's{nl}
Guardian, are you not?{waitkey}{clearbox}Can you not even come out{nl}
before us?{waitkey}{clearbox}Heehee... perhaps that{nl}
can't be helped?{waitkey}{clearbox}A tower Guardian is but a{nl}
small fry who can do nothing{nl}
without the Snow Queen's{waitkey}power, after all!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Yeah! Yeah!{nl}
You're too scared of Ayase{nl}
and friends to come out!{waitkey}{clearbox}Heh! Heh-heh!{nl}
Everyone! This tower's boss{nl}
seems kinda weak!{waitkey}{clearbox}Feels like we're super lucky!?{nl}
Kyahahaha!{waitkey}{ret}

???: Ohohohoho!{nl}
What well-barking little{nl}
puppies you are, for such{waitkey}fools!{waitkey}{clearbox}Truly... you seem worth{nl}
tormenting. Heehee...{waitkey}I shan't be bored, it seems!{waitkey}{clearbox}But you see! Bully an{nl}
opponent too weak and they{waitkey}break right away!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ufufu... I'm late with my{nl}
introduction. Do pardon me.{waitkey}{clearbox}I am charged by the "Snow{nl}
Queen" with guarding this{nl}
"Tower of Nemesis."{waitkey}{clearbox}I am "Michiko Matsudaira."{nl}
Do consider it an honor to{waitkey}die by my hand.{waitkey}{clearbox}By the way...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}... Oh?{nl}
You? {wait_fr:30}Yes, {wait_fr:30}you!!{nl}
My, my{waitkey}what have we here!{waitkey}{clearbox}Quite the handsome ma{wait_fr:30}n♥{waitkey}{clearbox}How about it? Rather than die{nl}
by my hand with that lot,{waitkey}won't you become my pet?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Wh{wait_fr:30}wh{wait_fr:30}whwh{wait_fr:30}whwhwh!{nl}
What did you say?!{nl}
Me? {wait_fr:30}You mean me?!{waitkey}{clearbox}A-and the pet of a woman{nl}
foul in character!{wait_fr:30} attitude!!{wait_fr:30}{nl}
and looks!!{waitkey}{clearbox}You want me to become your{nl}
lapdog?! Don't underestimate{nl}
Kei Nanjo!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll make you regret in hell{nl}
that you ever spoke to me so!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Fuga?!{nl}
Me? {wait_fr:30}You mean me??{nl}
Hold on just a second!{waitkey}{clearbox}What the heck! This hag!{nl}
Pops out of nowhere spouting{nl}
who-knows-what nonsense!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Don't screw with me!{nl}
Make "the great Brown"{nl}
your p-pet, you say?{waitkey}{clearbox}Don't mess around!!{nl}
Mocking me!! I'll pummel you!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll resculpt that ugly mug{nl}
of yours even uglier!{waitkey}{ret}

Michiko: Kiii!{nl}
Th-this Michiko{wait_fr:30}, after going{wait_fr:30}{nl}
out of her way to show{waitkey}you m-mercy!{waitkey}{clearbox}H-hmph!{nl}
Asking lowly creatures to{nl}
grasp my greatness was{waitkey}too much to ask, it seems.{waitkey}{clearbox}...Very well,{nl}
little puppies...{nl}
I shall break every last one{nl}
of you with my own hands...{waitkey}{clearbox}I've just lifted this tower's{nl}
time limit! Take as many{nl}
hours as you like!{waitkey}{clearbox}By any means, come to me!{waitkey}{clearbox}Understand? Take all the{nl}
hours you wish!{waitkey}{clearbox}Now then, I'll be waiting!!{nl}
Good day to you!!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: No time limit?{nl}
Given that woman's character,{nl}
there's something behind it.{waitkey}Don't you think?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Y'know, that Michiko{nl}
woman... she reminds me of{nl}
someone.{waitkey}Like how she's super stuck-up~{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What is with{nl}
that woman!?{nl}
Taking such a haughty,{nl}
condescending attitude!{waitkey}{clearbox}Who does she think she is!?{nl}
Does she imagine herself the{nl}
greatest in all the world?{waitkey}{clearbox}Unpleasant! Truly{nl}
unpleasant!!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: That haughty attitude{nl}
she seems to have been born{nl}
with...{waitkey}{clearbox}That brazen air, like she{nl}
thinks there's not a single{nl}
soul greater than herself!{waitkey}{clearbox}Just between us, that woman's{nl}
the spitting image of{nl}
a certain someone whose{nl}
name starts with N!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: No Time limit?{nl}
What could that mean?{waitkey}{clearbox}Is it that woman's confidence{nl}
that she can beat us easily{nl}
even without one?{waitkey}{clearbox}Or... is there some other{nl}
reason?{waitkey}{clearbox}Either way, there's surely{nl}
something behind it.{waitkey}{clearbox}The Time limit... we'd best{nl}
be more wary of it,{nl}
not less.{waitkey}{ret}
